sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant MobileApp
    participant Backend
    participant TokenChecker
    participant GoogleApple
    participant Commercetools
    participant EventSystem

    User->>MobileApp: Starts in-app purchase
    MobileApp->>Backend: Sends purchase info (price, course, platform, token)

    Backend->>Commercetools: Check if user already has a cart
    Commercetools-->>Backend: Return existing cart or none
    alt Cart exists
        Backend->>Commercetools: Delete old cart
    end

    Backend->>Commercetools: Create a new cart with course and price
    Commercetools-->>Backend: Return new cart

    Backend->>TokenChecker: Ask to validate the purchase token
    TokenChecker->>GoogleApple: Send token to Google or Apple
    GoogleApple-->>TokenChecker: Get token result

    TokenChecker->>Commercetools: Check if token was already used
    alt Token is already used
        TokenChecker-->>Backend: Tell backend it is a duplicate
        Backend->>Commercetools: Delete the new cart
        Backend-->>MobileApp: **Show error (payment already used)**
    else Token is valid
        TokenChecker-->>Backend: Send transaction info
    end

    Backend->>EventSystem: Send event - checkout started
    Backend->>EventSystem: Send event - item added to cart

    Backend->>Commercetools: Create a payment using the token info
    alt Payment creation failed
        Commercetools-->>Backend: **Error while creating payment**
        Backend-->>MobileApp: **Show error (payment creation failed)**
    else
        Commercetools-->>Backend: Return payment
        Backend->>EventSystem: Send event - payment method used

        Backend->>Commercetools: Attach payment to the cart
        alt Attaching payment failed
            Commercetools-->>Backend: **Error while attaching payment**
            Backend-->>MobileApp: **Show error (payment attach failed)**
        else
            Commercetools-->>Backend: Return updated cart

            Backend->>Commercetools: Create order from cart
            alt Order creation failed
                Commercetools-->>Backend: **Error while creating order**
                Backend-->>MobileApp: **Show error (order creation failed)**
            else
                Commercetools-->>Backend: Return order

                Backend->>Commercetools: Mark items as ready for delivery
                alt Updating item state failed
                    Commercetools-->>Backend: **Error while updating item states**
                    Backend-->>MobileApp: **Show error (item state update failed)**
                else
                    Commercetools-->>Backend: Return updated order

                    Backend->>EventSystem: Send event - order completed
                    Backend-->>MobileApp: Show success (order ID, number)
                end
            end
        end
    end
